OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,FA schoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,7,Ffrom a deodorant can, an inquest has
OL,8,Fheard.
OL,10,FTommie-Lee Gracie Billington was found
OL,11,Funresponsive next to a can of Lynx
OL,12,Fwhile at a sleepover at his friend's
OL,13,Fhouse in Lancaster on 1 March 2024.
OL,15,FThe two had enjoyed an evening of
OL,16,Fcomputer games before going to bed, an
OL,17,Finquest was told, but the next day
OL,18,FTommie-Lee was discovered by his
OL,19,Ffriend's mum and could not be woken.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
