PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,FDuring the inquest, the father of the
OL,7,Ffriend said that he had previously
OL,8,Fcaught both the boys inhaling fumes
OL,9,Ffrom deodorant cans before.
OL,11,FThe activity - often referred to as
OL,12,F'chroming' online - was explained by
OL,13,Fthe boy to cause a high and was an
OL,14,Factivity they did "for a laugh".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
