OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,FFollowing this incident, Tommie's
OL,7,Ffriend, who cannot be named for legal
OL,8,Freasons, told his parents he had
OL,9,Flearnt about the craze from an older
OL,10,Fboy at the local skatepark, and the
OL,11,Fissue was reported to the older boy's
OL,12,Fschool and the police.
OL,14,FThe boy's parents told the inquest
OL,15,Fthat Tommie-Lee's parents had been
OL,16,Finformed, but Sherri Ann Gracie and
OL,17,FGraham Billington, of Lancaster,
OL,18,Fdenied these claims, saying they were
OL,19,Fnever aware of the incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,FFriends of the boys told police the
OL,7,Ftwo youngsters had been on a video
OL,8,Fcall that night, where they showed
OL,9,Fthemselves inhaling the substances in
OL,10,Fa snapchat group call.
OL,12,FAccording to the boy's police
OL,13,Fstatement, Tommie had inhaled a full
OL,14,Fbottle of Lynx in the morning before
OL,15,Fdeciding to go to sleep.
OL,17,FHe was then found at 12pm unresponsive
OL,18,Fin a bunk bed before he died at Royal
OL,19,FLancaster Infirmary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
