OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,FDCI Dylan Hrynkwo, the senior officer
OL,7,Fon the day of the incident, said that
OL,8,Fwhen investigating the house, officers
OL,9,Ffound a bottle of Lynx in the bed and
OL,10,Fothers around the room.
OL,12,FFears of 'chroming' also led the
OL,13,Fpolice to investigate social media
OL,14,Fcontent and the boys' phones to see if
OL,15,Fthis had cause the boys to inhale the
OL,16,Fgases.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
