OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,FAfter only finding videos of people
OL,7,Fwarning others not to take part in the
OL,8,F'craze', DCI Hrynkwo suggested that
OL,9,Fsocial media did not encourage the
OL,10,Fboys to take part.
OL,12,FHowever, he added that "the internet
OL,13,Fis almost a living beast" and is
OL,14,Falways developing, meaning that videos
OL,15,Fpreviously may have been deleted if
OL,16,Fthey are deemed to be harmful.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,FDuring the inquest, family members
OL,7,Fshared their fond memories of Tommie-
OL,8,FLee, with his dad Graham saying: "I
OL,9,Fwill never forget him, he was such a
OL,10,Flovely boy". His Grandmother Tina
OL,11,FBurns added: "He was just a beautiful
OL,12,Fboy, he was our little whirlwind,
OL,13,Fthere was no stopping him. He was just
OL,14,Ffull of life, full of energy."
OL,16,FCoroner Emma Mather stated that Tommie-
OL,17,FLee's cause of death was inhalational
OL,18,Fasphyxiation and cardiac arrest after
OL,19,Finhaling butane and other 'volatile
OL,20,Fsubstances'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe concluded his death as
OL,7,Fmisadventure, as Tommie-Lee was deemed
OL,8,Fto be too young to have understood the
OL,9,Frisks.
OL,11,F"Tommy Lee was a beautiful little
OL,12,Fboy," she said: "He had his whole life
OL,13,Fahead of him.
OL,15,F"Both boys were playing video games
OL,16,Fand were observed by friends on a
OL,17,Fsnapchat call to be using aerosols. It
OL,18,Fis likely they were spraying aerosols
OL,19,Fthrough a towel and taking a deep
OL,20,Fbreath to experience the effects.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772451406
OL,3,CSchoolboy died after inhaling fumes
OL,4,Cfrom a deodorant can, inquest hears
OL,6,F"The boys had been able to inhale
OL,7,Faerosols without interruption. if the
OL,8,Fparents had been aware I have no doubt
OL,9,Fthey would have stepped in.
OL,11,F"I find that it is more likely than
OL,12,Fnot the two boys had been introduced
OL,13,Fto this by an older boy at the park.
OL,15,F"It is not possible to explain why
OL,16,Fthere was a missed opportunity to
OL,17,Finform Sherri Ann and Graham. It is my
OL,18,Ffinding that, had this happened,
OL,19,FTommie-Lees parents would have been
OL,20,Faware of this and would have spoke to
OL,21,Fhim about it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
